# ClickHouse on __KIT_NAME__ cluster

Workload: ClickHouse via Altinity Operator
Replicas: __REPLICAS__
Storage per replica: __STORAGE_SIZE__ (StorageClass: __STORAGE_CLASS_WFC__)
DB nodes: __DB_NODE_COUNT__
Region: __REGION__

## Quick start

```bash
easy-db-lab clickhouse start    # provision PVs, install operator, apply CR, wait for ready
easy-db-lab clickhouse stop     # remove CR (data retained on disk)
```

## Disk cleanup

To wipe ClickHouse data from all db nodes:

```bash
easy-db-lab cleanup clickhouse
```

